    "body": "This also affects the demolition units in the other mods, so no point adding the RA/TD/D2K/TS labels.\r\n\r\nOne solution could be to define a new interface that allows `AutoTarget` to know about and tell these special case traits to target an actor. The traits would need to expose some kind of \"AutoTargetCondition` so that the feature is enabled only if the aggressive stance condition is active.\r\n\r\n#16048 will be required before this could work properly."
